    <entry>
      <title>C++输入小写字母输出大写字母的几种思路</title>
      <link href="/2023/10/11/C++%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E5%B0%8F%E5%86%99%E5%AD%97%E6%AF%8D%E8%BE%93%E5%87%BA%E5%A4%A7%E5%86%99%E5%AD%97%E6%AF%8D%E7%9A%84%E5%87%A0%E7%A7%8D%E6%80%9D%E8%B7%AF/"/>
      <url>/2023/10/11/C++%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E5%B0%8F%E5%86%99%E5%AD%97%E6%AF%8D%E8%BE%93%E5%87%BA%E5%A4%A7%E5%86%99%E5%AD%97%E6%AF%8D%E7%9A%84%E5%87%A0%E7%A7%8D%E6%80%9D%E8%B7%AF/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="CPP中输入小写字母输出大写字母的几种思路"><a href="#CPP中输入小写字母输出大写字母的几种思路" class="headerlink" title="CPP中输入小写字母输出大写字母的几种思路"></a>CPP中输入小写字母输出大写字母的几种思路</h1><p>在C++编程中，我们有多种方法可以将小写字母转换为大写字母。以下是一些常见的方法：</p><h2 id="1-使用toupper函数"><a href="#1-使用toupper函数" class="headerlink" title="1. 使用toupper函数"></a>1. 使用toupper函数</h2><p>C++标准库中的 <code>&lt;cctype&gt;</code>头文件提供了一个名为 <code>toupper</code>的函数，可以将小写字母转换为大写字母。</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;cctype&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">char</span> lower = <span class="string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">char</span> upper = <span class="built_in">toupper</span>(lower);</span><br><span class="line">    std::cout &lt;&lt; upper &lt;&lt; std::endl;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="2-利用ASCII值"><a href="#2-利用ASCII值" class="headerlink" title="2. 利用ASCII值"></a>2. 利用ASCII值</h2><p>每个字符在计算机中都有一个对应的ASCII值。小写字母和大写字母之间的ASCII值差为32。因此，我们可以通过减去32将小写字母转换为大写字母。</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">char</span> lower = <span class="string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">char</span> upper = lower - <span class="number">32</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    std::cout &lt;&lt; upper &lt;&lt; std::endl;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="3-使用bitset"><a href="#3-使用bitset" class="headerlink" title="3. 使用bitset"></a>3. 使用bitset</h2><p>我们还可以使用位操作来实现这个转换。小写字母和大写字母在第五位上有所不同，我们可以通过改变这一位来实现转换。</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">char</span> lower = <span class="string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">char</span> upper = lower &amp; <span class="string">&#x27;_&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    std::cout &lt;&lt; upper &lt;&lt; std::endl;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>以上就是在C++中将小写字母转换为大写字母的几种常见方法。希望对你有所帮助！</p>]]></content>
      
      
